{"tid":1342704,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"建議飛天南安葬浩園","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T18:27:27.000Z","uid":254330,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"014d65c8f3f25b58919fb3a4d8bbe9726a4fe039","tid":1342704,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:52:26.000Z","msg":"元朗因為心臟病而死嘅叔父，為警隊賣命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議安葬於浩園，以表其榮！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81442072513f72ceb841ba44d24f689ad72795d","tid":1342704,"uid":254330,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:56:25.000Z","msg":"元朗叔父飛天南英勇地為警方執行職務，可惜不幸心臟病亡。黑社會也有愛國的，理應安葬浩園。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9cbfa64abe7736983b0309688c8c0fa2f73d19","tid":1342704,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://w.imag.cx/XTanx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fw.imag.cx%2FXTanx.png&h=8cecdab8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aeab9b55d07d9411baec3e94e9b0e6e4087215d7","tid":1342704,"uid":230911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4ed1a703b9a366b3499e3930feb8a05a10a5d3","tid":1342704,"uid":254330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:04:26.000Z","msg":"園內除了葬位及壁龕，亦設有刻有殉職人員姓名的紀念碑，以誌其捨身貢獻<br />\n<br />\n所有在執行職務時因「英勇過人行為」而喪生的公務員和非公務員，均可以獲得批准永久土葬<br />\n<br />\n飛天南受警犬委托，全心全意為警犬賣命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我建議特區政府應考慮其「英勇個人行為」而批准飛天南葬於具特別意義的浩園，以表其英勇事蹟！"},{"pid":"b8447033c6b7a481c944f35271d4fb4fd2752fa5","tid":1342704,"uid":277886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:06:17.000Z","msg":"特區明天要下半旗致哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df903f1bedc3434cc509cbfc8c2bc80b59f42fb5","tid":1342704,"uid":254330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:09:30.000Z","msg":"同時，本人警犬部門解散三合會及有組織罪案調查科。同時成立「三合會關係科」，於下次需要與黑社會合作行動時，先作出適當溝通及談論安家費問題，避免出現本次悲劇！"},{"pid":"e010ee4482cd63dc75e12ce71fc36e9b9c340d24","tid":1342704,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:10:08.000Z","msg":"改咗名做西天南喇"},{"pid":"30c971082c1f4658128b437ecbf5b5ebce8aebd3","tid":1342704,"uid":254330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e010ee4482cd63dc75e12ce71fc36e9b9c340d24","tid":1342704,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:10:08.000Z","msg":"改咗名做西天南喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:16:31.000Z","msg":"浩園乃是安葬英勇過人的公務員，<span style=\"color: red;\">飛天南接受警犬勾結，英勇地為警犬賣命</span>，可惜突然心臟病發身亡。<br />\n<br />\n豈由得你胡亂竄改姓名？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2d1572ead9a1e49c31e2f0976cbde070fb3933","tid":1342704,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:27:27.000Z","msg":"浩園，取其浩氣長存的意思。"}]}